<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Areas</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">London</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">London buildings don't wait — and neither do their move-in dates. We deliver building services right across London, from Cat-A landlord works and Cat-B fit-out to fabric, façades and external works, with one accountable team holding the programme. Services, space and building hand over together — on the date you planned back from.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about London →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">In London</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One team for the<br>whole building.</h2></div><p class="body" style="max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 32px;">From a City trading floor to a West End HQ or a Docklands tower, a London office touches every one of our trades at once — MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works. We're built for how central London actually works: occupied buildings handed over floor by floor, out-of-hours isolations, tight loading windows and limited access. One team plans around the live building, so the business keeps running while we do.</p><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>MEPH — HVAC, power, lighting &amp; public health</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cat A &amp; Cat B fit-out &amp; refurbishment</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cladding, roofing, render &amp; envelope</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Hard &amp; soft landscaping, surfacing, boundaries</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Areas we cover</div><h2 class="dhead sm">London &amp; the<br>surrounding area.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><span class="sector">City of London</span><span class="sector">Westminster</span><span class="sector">Canary Wharf</span><span class="sector">Shoreditch</span><span class="sector">Camden</span><span class="sector">Southwark</span><span class="sector">Islington</span><span class="sector">Hammersmith</span><span class="sector">Stratford</span><span class="sector">Croydon</span><span class="sector">Wandsworth</span><span class="sector">Hackney</span><span class="sector">Greenwich</span><span class="sector">Ealing</span></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Why AMPM</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Local, accountable,<br>one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>On your doorstep</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Out-of-hours and phased works in occupied buildings</strong> — floor-by-floor handover, temporary services and out-of-hours isolations that keep a live London building trading while we work.</li><li><strong>Logistics planned for central London</strong> — Congestion Charge and ULEZ routing, tight loading windows, restricted access and out-of-hours deliveries built into the programme, not bolted on.</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>One accountable team</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Tier-1 main-contractor experience</strong> — we run our packages to a main contractor's programme, RAMS and quality regime, and integrate cleanly on a busy London site.</li><li><strong>One team for services and fabric</strong> — MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works self-delivered under one accountable contractor, so the trades coordinate rather than collide.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">London questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover all of London?</summary><p>Yes — central London and Greater London, from the City, Westminster and the West End to Canary Wharf, Stratford, Croydon and the outer boroughs. We're based in Burgess Hill, West Sussex, an easy run up the M23 and direct on the Brighton main line, so London is squarely within our patch.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work out-of-hours in occupied City offices?</summary><p>Yes. Most of our central London work is phased around a live building — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services, night and weekend shifts and floor-by-floor handover — so the occupier keeps trading while we deliver. We plan the disruptive elements around the building's working day from the outset.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work for Tier-1 main contractors in London?</summary><p>Yes. We're set up to deliver packages under a Tier-1 main contractor — working to your programme, RAMS, quality and compliance regime, with one project manager accountable for our scope. We're comfortable on a busy multi-trade London site and integrate without friction.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top xlinks" data-xlink><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 22px;"><div class="kicker">Explore more</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Related across<br>AMPM Building&nbsp;Services.</h2></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Our service lines</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/meph/">MEPH</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/">Commercial Fit-out</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Envelope</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; External Works</a></div></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Sectors we serve</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/sectors/offices/">Commercial Offices</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/healthcare/">Healthcare</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/industrial/">Industrial &amp; Logistics</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/residential/">Residential &amp; BTR</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/">All sectors →</a></div></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Other areas</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/areas/crawley-gatwick/">Crawley &amp; Gatwick</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/brighton-hove/">Brighton &amp; Hove</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/guildford-surrey/">Guildford &amp; Surrey</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/">All areas →</a></div></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><a class="otherline" href="/commercial/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a><a class="otherline" href="/fabric/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a><a class="otherline" href="/groundworks/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "name": "Building services in London"